OL,3,CAm I entitled to a #1,000 payout for
OL,4,Cmy prepayment meter - and how do I
OL,5,Cclaim?
OL,7,FThe payouts follow an investigation by
OL,8,Fthe regulator into the forced fitting
OL,9,Fof prepayment meters, something that
OL,10,Fincreased two years ago during the
OL,11,Fcost of living crisis.
OL,13,FEnergy companies were found to be
OL,14,Fforcibly switching customers who were
OL,15,Fstruggling to pay their bills over to
OL,16,Fprepayment meters.
OL,18,FThis was a time when energy bills
OL,19,Fsharply increased as the global price
OL,20,Fof gas and oil was affected by
OL,21,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
