OL,4,Cmy prepayment meter - and how do I
OL,5,Cclaim?
OL,7,FOfgem said suppliers have committed to
OL,8,Fpay both additional compensation where
OL,9,Fit is due, and in some cases write off
OL,10,Fsome energy debt of customers who had
OL,11,Fan involuntary prepayment meter
OL,12,Finstalled during the assessment period
OL,13,Fof January 1, 2022 to January 31, 2023.
OL,15,FThe #74m compensation package is being
OL,16,Fsplit between eight suppliers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
