OL,4,Cmy prepayment meter - and how do I
OL,5,Cclaim?
OL,7,FHe said: "Our review also found wider
OL,8,Fissues with the processes suppliers
OL,9,Fhad in place, which is why we've put
OL,10,Fin place clearer, tougher rules to
OL,11,Fprotect customers in vulnerable
OL,12,Fsituations, and I'm pleased that from
OL,13,Ftoday suppliers will be applying our
OL,14,Fcompensation framework for those
OL,15,Fcustomers affected and have also
OL,16,Fcommitted to further support such as
OL,17,Fdebt write-off.
