OL,3,CAm I entitled to a #1,000 payout for
OL,4,Cmy prepayment meter - and how do I
OL,5,Cclaim?
OL,7,FReacting to today's news, the Energy
OL,8,FSecretary Ed Miliband claimed,
OL,9,F"justice is finally being delivered."
OL,11,FHe went on to add: "Consumers must
OL,12,Fcome first, which is why we are
OL,13,Freforming the energy market to stamp
OL,14,Fout bad practice and make it easier to
OL,15,Faccess proper redress when things go
OL,16,Fwrong, through our comprehensive
OL,17,Freview of Ofgem. This increased
OL,18,Fcompensation package is a good start,
OL,19,Fand we will be announcing further
OL,20,Freforms in the weeks ahead."
